    dc:description "Figure 7. Aora karibu n. sp.: male habitus 5.8 mm; A5antenna 1, 2; head with lateral lobe (×10); all mouthparts (×20): Md5mandible from both sides; Mx5maxilla 1, 2; UL5upper lip; LL5lower lip." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5220163/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5220165>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Aora karibu n. sp.: Gn5gnathopod 1 (×10), enlargement (×20); Gn2 (×10), enlargement (×20); Mxp5maxilliped (×20), palp and inner plate in enlargement (×40); U5uropod 3 (×10), enlargement of proximal part of peduncle (×40)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5220165/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

